<h1>Polls</h1>
<p>The polls home page displays a list of open polls.  To vote on a poll, simply click its title.</p>

<p>On the poll's voting page, simply answer any or all of the questions, and then click the &ldquo;Vote&rdquo; button to submit your responses.  Polls can contain a variety of answer types, including multiple choice and free response.</p>
